<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card border-success">
                <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
                    <h4 class="mb-0">
                        <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                        Welcome to EVE ESI Fleet Tool!
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="text-center mb-4">
                        <i class="bi bi-rocket-takeoff display-1 text-success"></i>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h5 class="card-title">Login Successful!</h5>
                    {{#if message}}
                    <div class="alert alert-info mb-4">
                        <i class="bi bi-info-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                        {{message}}
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Welcome{{#if nickname}}, <strong>{{nickname}}</strong>{{/if}}! Your Discord account has been successfully registered to our fleet management system. 
                        To get started, you'll need to link your EVE Online character(s).
                    </p>

                    <div class="alert alert-info mt-4">
                        <h6 class="alert-heading">
                            <i class="bi bi-info-circle-fill me-2"></i>
                            Next Steps:
                        </h6>
                        <ol class="mb-0">
                            <li>Open Discord and go to our server</li>
                            <li>Use the <code>/link</code> command in any channel</li>
                            <li>Follow the prompts to authenticate your EVE Online character(s)</li>
                            <li>Once linked, you'll be able to interact with the fleets as they are created!</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>

                    <div class="alert alert-warning mt-4">
                        <h6 class="alert-heading">
                            <i class="bi bi-lightbulb-fill me-2"></i>
                            Pro Tips:
                        </h6>
                        <ul class="mb-0">
                            <li>You can link multiple EVE characters to your account</li>
                            <li>Make sure to link your main fleet character first</li>
                            <li>Keep your EVE Online tokens active to maintain access</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer bg-light">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                        <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-success">
                            <i class="bi bi-house-door me-2"></i>
                            Go to Home Page
                        </a>
                        <small class="text-muted">Need help? Contact an administrator.</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
